COVID-19 Status 💉 🦠

As of 9:36PM PT today, over 1.6 million Canadians have tested positive for COVID-19. Sadly, 27.5 thousand have died.

In the last day, 4 thousand new infections were reported and 50 deaths. This is trending downwards.

Fortunately, 55.4 million doses of the vaccine have been administered. For those 12 years and older, 86.6% have their 1st shot and 79.7% are fully vaccinated!

Vaccination is speeding up, but there are 8.5 million doses in the freezer. It currently takes ~87 days for new deliveries to get into arms.

At the current rate, Canadians should achieve herd immunity around Nov-21 when 80% of the entire population is fully vaccinated. There is no approved vaccine for children aged 11 or younger.
